query:
INSERT INTO propertyImages (propertyId, imageUrl) 
SELECT p.id, CASE 
  WHEN p.id % 8 = 1 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502672260266-1c1ef2d93688?w=800&h=600&fit=crop'
  WHEN p.id % 8 = 2 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522708323590-d24dbb6b0267?w=800&h=600&fit=crop'
  WHEN p.id % 8 = 3 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560448204-e02f11c3d0e2?w=800&h=600&fit=crop'
  WHEN p.id % 8 = 4 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556909114-f6e7ad7d3136?w=800&h=600&fit=crop'
  WHEN p.id % 8 = 5 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1570129477492-45a003537e1f?w=800&h=600&fit=crop'
  WHEN p.id % 8 = 6 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1493857671505-72967e2e2760?w=800&h=600&fit=crop'
  WHEN p.id % 8 = 7 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512917774080-9b274b3f5798?w=800&h=600&fit=crop'
  ELSE 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505873242700-f289a29e7e0f?w=800&h=600&fit=crop'
END as imageUrl
FROM properties p
WHERE p.id > 8 AND p.id NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT propertyId FROM propertyImages);
